00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:57.920
and your thinking on both sides,
what you put into the computer

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.290
and what you get out.

00:05:59.290 --> 00:06:01.837
He also said what are the
most important problems

00:06:01.837 --> 00:06:02.420
