00:49:33.950 --> 00:49:35.390
How could they vary differently?

00:49:35.390 --> 00:49:36.140
The answer is yes.

00:49:44.080 --> 00:49:46.200
This is a cruise
through phase space.

00:49:46.200 --> 00:49:48.000
Gamma is always the origin.

00:49:48.000 --> 00:49:50.640
