00:50:23.770 --> 00:50:25.380
that you could have?

00:50:25.380 --> 00:50:25.890
Why not?

00:50:30.990 --> 00:50:33.108
Tell me why not.

00:50:33.108 --> 00:50:35.400
AUDIENCE: If you choose a
different path, [INAUDIBLE]..

00:50:35.400 --> 00:50:37.800
JEFFREY C. GROSSMAN: If you
