and doesn't change anymore

00:56:20.110 --> 00:56:22.450
if the band structure--
if properties of the band

00:56:22.450 --> 00:56:24.040
structure are what I want.

00:56:24.040 --> 00:56:28.050
That's how many k-points I need.

00:56:28.050 --> 00:56:29.610
Does everybody see that?

00:56:29.610 --> 00:56:30.600
That's the difference.

